            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The alkali targets (Li,Na and K) were made from natural",
                "metals, rolled to thicknesses of 5 to 8 mg/cm2",
                "between 1/4 mil Mylar sheets.",
                "Self-supporting boron targets of 4 to 10 mg/cm2 were",
                "prepared from a suspension from amorphous B-11 (98.63%",
                "enrichment) in benzene containing a group of",
                "polystyrene solution to serve as a binding agent."
              ]
            }
          ],
